headline: Stryker to announce financial results for its first quarter of fiscal year 2025
summary: Portage, Michigan, April 07, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Stryker (NYSE:SYK) announced that it will report financial results for its first quarter of fiscal year 2025 on Thursday, May 1, 2025. A press release will be issued at approximately 4:05 p.m. ET and available at Stryker - Press Releases that day.
